<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8334303>
    dc:description "FIGURE 17. Falconina spp.: A, B Falconina iza sp. nov., male holotype (MCN 10.582): A palp, ventral view; B palp, retrolateral view. C, D Falconina catirina sp. nov., male holotype (MPEG 37219): C palp, ventral view; D palp, retrolateral view. Abbreviations AS, apical spur; C, conductor; CRP, cymbial retrolateral basal process; E, embolus; EP, embolar process; dVL, dorsal lobe of the ventral lobe of the retrolateral tibial apophysis; DL, dorsal lobe of the retrolateral tibial apophysis; ML, median lobe of the retrolateral tibial apophysis; TP, tegular process; VL, ventral lobe of the retrolateral tibial apophysis. Scale bar 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8334303/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8334305>
    dc:description "FIGURE 18. Falconina spp.:A, B Falconina iza sp. nov., male holotype (MCN 10.582):A palp, ventral view; B palp, retrolateral view. C, D Falconina catirina sp. nov., male holotype (MPEG 37219): A palp, ventral view; B palp, retrolateral view. Scale bar 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8334305/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

